        <specpara>
            <warning>
                <para>Shut off and bleed the air system to prevent lines from whipping.</para>
            </warning>
        </specpara>
        <para>Remove the spear rod. Remove the remote control assembly from the unit and out of the vehicle (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f1302205">Figure 5</hotlnk>). Remove the wire harness. Check components for damage.
        </para>
